{"tid":1812270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"破局唯一方法，係搞到商場好似花市咁迫，港豬走自己都走，港豬返黎自己又返黎，唯一缺撼係好難夠人做","createTime":"2020-01-05T11:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T12:16:37.000Z","uid":31215,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0a07f4aa5bc84dc65fb95e863e0dab0e6a941c3a","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:02:58.000Z","msg":"Be water be shapeless<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢圍捕係冇得破架喇<br />\n班柒頭都唔要面<br />\n唯有令濫捕成為成個運動最強攬炒工具<br />\n令佢投鼠忌器<br />\n<br />\n今日啲狗最唔知點做嘅時刻<br />\n係成班手足遊行完<br />\n似走非走<br />\n拎住標語好似去緊搭巴士<br />\n又好似係仍然示緊威<br />\n趕又唔係，唔趕又唔係<br />\n<br />\n而最清𥇦嘅時刻<br />\n係佢警告市民非法集結<br />\n市民仍然唔走屌返佢轉頭<br />\n佢就肯定呢班人八成都係手足<br />\n有兩成無辜都唔理<br />\n<br />\n之後要贏<br />\n有兩個條件<br />\n第一個係模糊<br />\n第二個係糢糊得來破壞性大<br />\n<br />\n以前和你shop<br />\n但用嗌口號同滋擾性行為癱瘓<br />\n破壞性大但唔糢糊<br />\n佢拉就好容易<br />\n<br />\n但如果今日元朗人數<br />\n去商場等人，或者出出入入，搞到花市咁迫<br />\n商場一定迫到做唔到生意<br />\nPopo一係警告，一係直接拉<br />\n佢警告咪成個商場一齊走，直接拉嘅話成個商場陪葬我又唔怕呀<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦<br />\n如果咁shapeless<br />\n你點知邊啲係手足<br />\n會唔會到時好多人真shop，自己on99？<br />\n<br />\n會咁問就係因為唔夠人<br />\n你遊行去搭車<br />\n大家冇記認<br />\n你都知成車都係自己人<br />\n<br />\n你中環集會<br />\n大家放工裝，你都知成個地鐵站都係自己人去同一個地方<br />\n<br />\n之前812機場和你飛<br />\n你都知成個機場係手足唔係旅客<br />\n機場巴士上嘅都係手足唔係旅客<br />\n<br />\n點解呀？<br />\n因為最無形但突出嘅記認<br />\n係不正常而特別多嘅人流<br />\n<br />\n嗰個地方多人到唔正常<br />\n你就知成功<br />\n覺得得自己on99<br />\n你就知fail左<br />\n<br />\n呢種戰略歷史上只成功過一次<br />\n就係爆眼後嘅機場和你飛<br />\n純粹用人數癱瘓機場<br />\n混和旅客搞到popo做唔到野<br />\n睇住最後一班機時間一齊走<br />\n<br />\n不過呢招都唔係我第一個提架喇<br />\n只係大家好似好憎和你shop<br />\n叫極都唔出黎<br />\n淨係鍾意遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家又好似驚人唔知自己有份示威<br />\n著得又似，又鍾意唔走屌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020喺商場從現一次812和你飛奇蹟<br />\n可以嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/2400/1*CZavKLToNipikJGZaqlOZw@2x.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F2400%2F1%2ACZavKLToNipikJGZaqlOZw%402x.jpeg&h=ee00d960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fortuneinsight.com/web/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/hong-kong-airport-travel.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffortuneinsight.com%2Fweb%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2Fhong-kong-airport-travel.jpg&h=b4749e39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/08/20190812_po_%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F08%2F20190812_po_%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA2.jpg&h=98c1e5e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S0mDkjk0n.QvhYcN16irAQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/03885360e0282bef398c3fe29b28f11d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FS0mDkjk0n.QvhYcN16irAQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2F03885360e0282bef398c3fe29b28f11d&h=e446073a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/08/20190812_po_%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F08%2F20190812_po_%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA.jpg&h=fc10b554&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS<br />\n其中一張相係某年復活節出境人流<br />\n睇落佢地都幾似示威者我就貼埋出黎<br />\n應該話睇落示威者都幾似佢地先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83c1d88153e344f60241c6d911058b7868ec389","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed4f3c7bba46f38fec67aafc42e2603d0bfce08","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdca8a40ea244353975a3afa5c40a1d7f011449","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5959858d6d11e2554e97705dd7e7355ea5b62b","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee62237784823c8cf5baa35802f605f87c3e1034","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:06:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be777dd1c45e792d53e716bc1fd34e7bb2dec30","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8ac31b89d090c4eadeee125dd9ce289cf44974","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1f4985c4b3c529a79e655483d2ab7ec5fc1437","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46028e8c535e6c46bb820566ac09a1abd9677497","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:07:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da344b02145d6484b23c21aaa86dee19ebe3933a","tid":1812270,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"大家千其唔好<br />\n支持黃色經濟圈<br />\n堅持經濟攬抄<br />\n商家冇生意做好慘<br />\n和你shop,和你唱 ,和你lunch搞到人冇生意就唔好啦<br />\n紅日,新年,復活做唔到生意好慘架<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可，鬥長命<br />\n香港四大中資企業分別係<br />\n中旅、華潤、招商、中國光大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94daf92819a4d11b6469c6f568c519272274883","tid":1812270,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:09:44.000Z","msg":"集中去藍店藍絲集中地，等佢濫捕藍絲"},{"pid":"67189d2ce74442170ff6cdf43dbda551a6d1f89f","tid":1812270,"uid":84176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:10:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec3f6cc351876fec554773d65d342b675eb65156","tid":1812270,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:11:25.000Z","msg":"各位手足，同意與否，請聽我一言，睇哂佢，Spread出去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1812233/page/1#preview\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1812233/page/1#preview</a><br />\n<br />\n我P牌推唔到 唯有咁樣推比大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c59cec7e14535e0c995d54cec33045d2ee349f","tid":1812270,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"商場多狗到唔洗入"},{"pid":"bba431fcb75595c8c7bd055e5a041274c57fc4bd","tid":1812270,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"popo會有十幾分鐘警告人走，就係叫嗰啲唔關事既走。淨返嗰啲就拉。藍屍同唔係遊行嗰啲人已經一早走曬，仲點攬炒？"},{"pid":"f8382481fe331c2f77fae940a7b3c5d405f4a713","tid":1812270,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bba431fcb75595c8c7bd055e5a041274c57fc4bd","tid":1812270,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"popo會有十幾分鐘警告人走，就係叫嗰啲唔關事既走。淨返嗰啲就拉。藍屍同唔係遊行嗰啲人已經一早走曬，仲點攬炒？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T11:20:52.000Z","msg":"個個走哂<br />\n佢又走你又走<br />\n仲唔係攬炒咩"},{"pid":"67fa5d9cfc835edc9560016496d7e1546fd3f6c3","tid":1812270,"uid":321345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"repl